summary: I am a disciplined worker interested in the field of neurology and cardiology. I have a great amount of perseverance and like to keep developing myself at all times. My eagerness to learn and curiosity contribute well to this. My main aim for the future is to work at a research institute to contribute to disease-related research. My passion is to be able to use my research to improve the lives of patients.
